label: "Sixty-Fifth Annual Meeting. South Carolina Federation of Women's and Girl's Clubs. 1909-1974"
description: South Carolina Federation of Women's and Girls' Clubs' Sixty-Fifth Annual Meeting publication. Publication contains program of events, photographs of club members in various locations around South Carolina, information on members and subgroups, and advertisements.
